Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:18.45,Default JP,,0,0,0,,それでは  これより
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:18.45,Default CN,,0,0,0,,那麼接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:21.22,Default JP,,0,0,0,,みなさんが仕上げたケーキを  いただきましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:21.22,Default CN,,0,0,0,,就請大家品嘗自己親手做的蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:22.97,Default JP,,0,0,0,,やった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:22.97,Default CN,,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:24.92,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ついに  待ちに待ったこの瞬間がやってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:24.92,Default CN,,0,0,0,,就等著這一刻呢 可算來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:29.85,Default JP,,0,0,0,,もう...まったく
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:29.85,Default CN,,0,0,0,,哎...真是夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:30.92,Default JP,,0,0,0,,食欲半減よ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:30.92,Default CN,,0,0,0,,看著就倒了一半胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:32.15,Default JP,,0,0,0,,大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:32.15,Default CN,,0,0,0,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:35.60,Default JP,,0,0,0,,見た目は悪くても  心がこもってるから味は同じだって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:35.60,Default CN,,0,0,0,,就算樣子醜 裡面的味道還是一樣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:37.25,Default JP,,0,0,0,,本当？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:37.25,Default CN,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:40.15,Default JP,,0,0,0,,そう  大事なのは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:40.15,Default CN,,0,0,0,,是啊 重點在於
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:43.82,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ケーキを作る人たちの気持ちがひとつになっているかどうかって事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:43.82,Default CN,,0,0,0,,做蛋糕的人彼此間有沒有默契嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:45.25,Default JP,,0,0,0,,いい  志穂  莉奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:45.25,Default CN,,0,0,0,,聽好了 志穗 莉奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.82,0:11:47.42,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ケーキ作りも  ラクロスも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.82,0:11:47.42,Default CN,,0,0,0,,做蛋糕也好 袋棍球也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:50.80,Default JP,,0,0,0,,一番大切なのは  仲間同士のハーモニカなんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:50.80,Default CN,,0,0,0,,最重要的都是同伴間的口琴配合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:56.37,PS,,0,0,0,,{\fs27}渚的口誤：“ハーモニカ ”是“口琴”,“ハーモニー”才是“和諧\協調\默契”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:52.35,Default JP,,0,0,0,,...は？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:52.35,Default CN,,0,0,0,,...哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:56.30,Default JP,,0,0,0,,...それを言うなら「ハーモニー」でしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:56.30,Default CN,,0,0,0,,...應該是“默契”吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:58.92,Default JP,,0,0,0,,大切なのは  「調和」ですわ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:58.92,Default CN,,0,0,0,,“協調”是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.70,Default JP,,0,0,0,,みんなで力を合わせて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.70,Default CN,,0,0,0,,大家齊心協力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:04.25,Default JP,,0,0,0,,美しい「ハーモニー」~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:04.25,Default CN,,0,0,0,,就是美好的“和諧”呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:05.32,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なぎさ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:05.32,Default CN,,0,0,0,,渚！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:08.22,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なによ  ほのかまでケーキに文句言うつもり？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:08.22,Default CN,,0,0,0,,幹嘛呀 穗乃香你也要挑這個蛋糕的毛病？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:09.30,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ほら  あれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:09.30,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你看 那個！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:13.67,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あ  あれは...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:13.67,Default CN,,0,0,0,,那 那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:16.52,Default JP,,0,0,0,,もしかして？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:16.52,Default CN,,0,0,0,,難道說？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:17.42,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なぎさ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:17.42,Default CN,,0,0,0,,渚！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.55,Default JP,,0,0,0,,雪城さん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.55,Default CN,,0,0,0,,雪城同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:21.37,Default JP,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:21.37,Default CN,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:22.82,Default JP,,0,0,0,,どうしました？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:22.82,Default CN,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.15,0:12:24.15,Default JP,,0,0,0,,いえ  別に...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.15,0:12:24.15,Default CN,,0,0,0,,沒 沒什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:26.02,Default JP,,0,0,0,,では席に戻りなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:26.02,Default CN,,0,0,0,,那就回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:26.78,Default JP,,0,0,0,,はい...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:26.78,Default CN,,0,0,0,,好...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:29.52,Default JP,,0,0,0,,甘い香りが堪らないですわ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:29.52,Default CN,,0,0,0,,這味道甜甜的 真好聞呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:32.52,Default JP,,0,0,0,,いただきますー
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:32.52,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我開動了——
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:37.50,Default JP,,0,0,0,,美味しい！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:37.50,Default CN,,0,0,0,,好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:39.57,Default JP,,0,0,0,,確かに見た目は悪いけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:39.57,Default CN,,0,0,0,,雖然看起來是醜了點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.45,Default JP,,0,0,0,,味は最高  最高  最高！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.45,Default CN,,0,0,0,,但味道超棒超棒超棒的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:43.60,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ほのか  嫌な感じがするミポ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:43.60,Default CN,,0,0,0,,穗乃香 我有不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:45.87,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ミップル
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:45.87,Default CN,,0,0,0,,米普魯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:46.97,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なぎさ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:46.97,Default CN,,0,0,0,,渚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:49.00,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なぎさ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:49.00,Default CN,,0,0,0,,渚！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:51.37,Default JP,,0,0,0,,何なの？今  忙しいんだから！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:51.37,Default CN,,0,0,0,,幹嘛呀？忙著呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:53.22,Default JP,,0,0,0,,闇の気配を感じるメポ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:53.22,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我感受到了黑暗的氣息呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:54.17,Default JP,,0,0,0,,嘘でしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:54.17,Default CN,,0,0,0,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:55.97,Default JP,,0,0,0,,すぐ近くにいるメポ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:55.97,Default CN,,0,0,0,,距離很近！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:12:58.87,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ベローネ学院に通っていたころ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:12:58.87,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我以前在菲諾奈學院讀書的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:01.48,Default JP,,0,0,0,,この近くのケーキ工場に来た事があってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:01.48,Default CN,,0,0,0,,到這附近的蛋糕工廠參觀過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:03.45,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ケーキ工場？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:03.45,Default CN,,0,0,0,,蛋糕工廠？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:05.70,Default JP,,0,0,0,,その時  この公園を見つけたの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:05.70,Default CN,,0,0,0,,這公園就是我在那時候發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:07.42,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なかなかいい所でしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:07.42,Default CN,,0,0,0,,是個不錯的地方吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.77,0:13:08.55,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ええ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.77,0:13:08.55,Default CN,,0,0,0,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.80,Default JP,,0,0,0,,じゃあ  もしかして...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.80,Default CN,,0,0,0,,那 難道...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:12.86,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なぎささんたちも  この近くに...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:12.86,Default CN,,0,0,0,,渚她們就在這附近...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:14.36,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ひかり  ひかり！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:14.36,Default CN,,0,0,0,,光 光！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:15.55,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ポルン？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:15.55,Default CN,,0,0,0,,保倫？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:17.05,Default JP,,0,0,0,,プリキュラが危険だポポ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:17.05,Default CN,,0,0,0,,Precura有危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:18.07,Default JP,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:18.07,Default CN,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:22.40,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ここだったら  結構お客さんが集まるんじゃないかって睨んでるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:22.40,Default CN,,0,0,0,,在這裡應該能招攬到不少客人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.15,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.15,Default CN,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:26.45,Default JP,,0,0,0,,...ひかり？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:26.45,Default CN,,0,0,0,,...光？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:32.48,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あ～美味しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:32.48,Default CN,,0,0,0,,哎呀~真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:36.87,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ま  まさか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:36.87,Default CN,,0,0,0,,難 難道？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:42.90,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なぎさとメップルはどこミポ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:42.90,Default CN,,0,0,0,,渚和梅普魯在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:44.17,Default JP,,0,0,0,,待ちなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:44.17,Default CN,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:44.90,Default JP,,0,0,0,,急ぐメポ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:44.90,Default CN,,0,0,0,,快呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:46.80,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なぎさ  どこなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:46.80,Default CN,,0,0,0,,渚 你在哪裡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:50.84,Monster JP,,0,0,0,,ザケンナー
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:50.84,Monster CN,,0,0,0,,搞事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:13:58.95,Default JP,,0,0,0,,危ないミポ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:13:58.95,Default CN,,0,0,0,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:08.60,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ほのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:08.60,Default CN,,0,0,0,,穗乃香！
