Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:49.72,Default CN,,0,0,0,,White
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:05.50,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ホワイト！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:05.50,Default CN,,0,0,0,,White！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:09.55,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ホワイトに何すんのよ？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:09.55,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你對White做了什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:19.20,Default JP,,0,0,0,,そろそろ終わりにするよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:19.20,Default CN,,0,0,0,,也差不多該結束了！
